=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies the configuration of a Kubernetes C<hostPath> volume. A
C<hostPath> volume mounts an existing file or directory from the host
node's filesystem into your pod. For more information, see hostPath
(https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/storage/volumes/#hostpath) in the
I<Kubernetes documentation>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Path => Str

The path of the file or directory on the host to mount into containers
on the pod.



